title: Ep. XXX – Just A Little Chat
description: Having a quick chat with our good friend Jordan Jensen as we plan for this weekends episode. Thanks to everyone who checked out the episode this week on patreon.com/tafs. Very nice to be excited about something again lol. I'll be at the Irvine Improv aug 18-20, come out bring your friends, say hi, come chat after etc
